A man was shot dead and a woman was stabbed in an apparent armed robbery at a restaurant in Hobart Road, in Bryanston, Johannesburg, on Saturday afternoon, paramedics said. ER24, Life Healthcare, CoJ, and other services attended to the incident, ER24 spokeswoman Chitra Bodasing-Harduth said. Upon arrival paramedics found a man who had been shot lying outside a restaurant. ER24 paramedics along with other services initiated CPR [cardiopulmonary resuscitation]. However, despite all efforts, the man died. A woman who was stabbed was treated for minor injuries and transported to hospital for further care by ER24. The exact details surrounding the incident are unknown. Authorities were on [the] scene for further investigations, Bodasing-Harduth said.